function onReceiveMIDI(message, connections) --print('onReceiveMIDI') --print('\t message =', table.unpack(message)) --print('\t connections =', table.unpack(connections)) -- relay all info from the keyboard to the synth on connection 4 --if connections[2] == true then -- relay all info from the Bridge to the synth on connection 4 -- print('\t sent midiMessage 1 to 4') -- sendMIDI({ message[1], message[2], message[3] }, { false, false, false, true }) if connections[3] == true then -- relay all info from the keyboard to the synth on connection 4 --print('\t sent midiMessage 3 to 4 & 5') sendMIDI({ message[1], message[2], message[3] }, { false, false, false, true, true }) elseif connections[2] == true then --print('\t sent midiMessage 2 to 4 & 5') --sendMIDI({ message[1], message[2], message[3] }, { false, false, false, true, true }) elseif connections[4] == true then print('\t sent midiMessage 4 to 4 & 5') sendMIDI({ message[1], message[2], message[3] }, { false, false, false, true, true }) elseif connections[5] == true then print('\t sent midiMessage 5 to 4 & 5') sendMIDI({ message[1], message[2], message[3] }, { false, false, false, true, true }) end end
function onReceiveOSC(message, connections) print('onReceiveOSC') local path = message[1] local arguments = message[2] print('\t path =', path) for i=1,#arguments do print('\t argument =', arguments[i].tag, arguments[i].value) end print('\t connections =', table.unpack(connections)) end
function onReceiveGamepad(input, value, connections) print('onReceiveGamepad') print('\t input =', input) -- one of the GamepadInput enumeration values print('\t value =', value) print('\t connections =', table.unpack(connections)) end
function onReceiveNotify(key, value) print('onReceiveNotify') print('\t key =', key) print('\t value =', value) end

function onValueChanged(key) if(tonumber(self.parent.children.SynthLabel.properties.tag) == 1) then if(self.values.x == 1) then self.parent.children.EnabledLabel_1.values.text = 'Enabled' else self.parent.children.EnabledLabel_1.values.text = 'Disabled' end else if(self.values.x == 1) then self.parent.children.EnabledLabel_2.values.text = 'Enabled' else self.parent.children.EnabledLabel_2.values.text = 'Disabled' end end end
